<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE ANGELS' SONG</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zan khang lai a thawm hunggi chuh,
 Van la gi hawih lopi chuh ahi;
 Lapawl ngaihnawpum chuh ahi,
 La sa chuh Angel thiengte ahiu.

[V2]
 &quot;Chungnungpena lopi hen la!
 Lei chung ah kichamna thu luong hen!&quot;
 Kumsawt in zie thu hi thang hen,
 Lei kipahna'n hung dim hen.

[V3]
 2. Belamchingte'n lopi a muu,
 Angelte thuphuon chuh a zau ie;
 Gankuong ah khun in chibai ui;
 La hawih chun gamtin a thawn laiin.

[V4]
 3. Hukdampa Pathien sathau nuh,
 I leibat lauhum din di'n A hung;
 Mi lungkhampa leh mi deihloh,
 Balam No I gitloh lamangpa.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>53</hymn_number>
</song>